<p><b><font size=+3>5.3 Component Integration</font></b></center>

<ol><b><font size=+1>Office Application Integration</font></b>
<ol>&nbsp;
<br><font size=+1>--Integrate software systems on the personal desktop
computer.</font>
<br><font size=+1>--Ex:</font>
<ol><font size=+1>Integrates Visio drawing application, Microsoft Word,
and Microsoft's Internet Explorer into one user interface.</font></ol>
</ol>

<p><br><font size=+1>Limitation:</font>
<ol><font size=+1>1. Limited to the integration on personal computers.
Heterogeneours environments are not supported.</font>
<br><font size=+1>2. Limited to a small number of components.</font></ol>
</ol>

